    <item>
      <title>中国银行降低了消费者贷款利率，以记录刺激需求的低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/china-banks-cut-consumer-loan-rates-to-record-low-to-spur-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国银行正在削减消费贷款的利率，以记录低谷，因为决策者不断增加刺激措施以稳定增长并反击美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/china-banks-cut-consumer-loan-rates-to-record-low-to-spur-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曼谷航空公司寻求30架新喷气机，因为白莲花提升了旅游</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/white-lotus-effect-bangkok-airways-to-buy-more-planes-on-thailand-tourism-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼谷航空公司PCL正在准备订购多达30架新飞机，因为它更新了老化的舰队，并计划在电视连续剧《白莲花》的受欢迎程度上推动旅游业提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/white-lotus-effect-bangkok-airways-to-buy-more-planes-on-thailand-tourism-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚可能会持有股票的税率，贸易动荡威胁着印第安纳州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/indonesia-may-hold-rate-as-stocks-trade-turmoil-threaten-rupiah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚的中央银行可能将其关键利率保持不变，以支持卢比亚，在美国资深财政部长被迫否认辞职的谣言中宣布股票投掷后，选择了稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/indonesia-may-hold-rate-as-stocks-trade-turmoil-threaten-rupiah</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
